          <div class="trust-stack">
            <article><span>01</span><div><h3>Initial video inspection</h3><p>We assess the pipe condition and locate blockages using a high-definition camera before any jetting begins. This ensures we use the right nozzle and pressure for your specific situation.</p></div></article>
            <article><span>02</span><div><h3>Hydro jetting application</h3><p>High-pressure water clears debris, grease, scale, and roots based on inspection findings. We match nozzle and pressure to the pipe: chain knocker for scale, flushing for grease, root cutter for sewer lines.</p></div></article>
            <article><span>03</span><div><h3>Final inspection</h3><p>A post-clean camera confirms pipes are clear and documents the pipe condition. We provide maintenance recommendations to keep your drains flowing.</p></div></article>
